        <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
            
            <p>Samuel Wolchok was born in Russia in 1896 and emigrated to the United States in 1912.
                Wolchok was President of the Untied Retail, Wholesale and Department Store Employees
                Union from 1937 to 1948. After his presidency, he worked for the CIO and later in
                industry. He died at the age of 82 in 1979.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            
            <p>This collection consists of proceedings of the United Retail, Wholesale and
                Department Store Employes Union's General Executive Board meetings from 1945 through
                1948, and correspondence, clippings, and memorabilia of President Samuel
                Wolchok.</p>
        </scopecontent>
